collections.name: Spring Framework Exercise Base Tests
collections.description:
## Spring Framework Exercise Base Tests
These are the base scripts used to test Spring Framework Exercises

folders.name: Add a Customer
folders.description:
1. Add a customer (happy path)
2. Missing fields
    1. firstName
    2. secondName
    3. birthDate
3. Invalid date format
    1. YYYYMMDD
    2. DDMMYYYY
    3. MMDDYYYY
    4. YYYY-MM-DD
    5. DD-MM-YYYY
    6. MM-DD-YYYY
    7. DD/MM/YYYY
    8. MM/DD/YYYY
    9. DD/MM/YY
    10. MM/DD/YY
    11. 2000/04/31
4. Duplicate customer
